metadata.name: ARIES
metadata.description: Aries are people full of energy and enthusiasm for life. Adventurous by nature, they love challenges, freedom and new ideas, so they are never afraid of beginnings or new stages. They will always fight if they think the cause is worth it. They are leaders and prefer to give orders to receive them. The energy that emanates from them leads them to be somewhat aggressive, stubborn and restless.
